        "content": "Web search results for query: \"\"full AI IDE\" launch 2025 Product Hunt\"\n\nI'll search for information about a \"full AI IDE\" launch on Product Hunt in 2025.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"2025年ProductHunt创造者的可视化年终总结 | ProductHunt 今日热榜 - 12月28日\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/sahadev_/article/details/156354284\"},{\"title\":\"Google Vids：由AI驱动的工作视频创作| ProductHunt 今日热榜\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/u011064099/article/details/155930865\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-11-20\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/a7574733657592594985/\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-11-20\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/Jackxiaochen/article/details/155071197\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-11-18\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/Jackxiaochen/article/details/154995525\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-10-05\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7557661514006594048/\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜| 2025-10-05 原创\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/Jackxiaochen/article/details/152558701\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-09-16\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7550868256492438068/\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜| 2025-08-28 原创 - CSDN博客\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/Jackxiaochen/article/details/150957158\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2025-08-26\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/Jackxiaochen/article/details/150863448\"}]\n\nBased on my web search, I found several AI IDEs launched on Product Hunt in 2025. Here are the key results:\n\n## **AI IDEs Launched on Product Hunt in 2025:**\n\n### **1. Dropstone**\n- **Launch Date:** Early October 2025\n- **Concept:** A self-improving AI IDE with autonomous programming capabilities\n- **Key Features:**\n  - Desktop application\n  - Computer use API integration\n  - Ollama models support\n  - Claude Code integration\n  - Agent mode\n  - Recursive generation capabilities\n- **Reception:** 135 upvotes\n\n### **2. RightNow AI Code Editor**\n- **Launch Date:** October 2025\n- **Concept:** GPU-native AI code editor\n- **Key Features:**\n  - CUDA programming support\n  - Real-time performance analysis\n  - AI optimization\n  - GPU virtualization\n  - Full-featured simulator\n- **Reception:** 284 upvotes (Featured)\n\n### **3. Oppla AI IDE**\n- **Launch Date:** August 27, 2025\n- **Concept:** Context-focused AI Integrated Development Environment\n- **Key Features:**\n  - Context building and maintenance\n  - Not limited to just code writing\n  - Unrestricted building capabilities\n  - Persistent context that evolves\n- **Reception:** 117 upvotes\n\n### **4. Qoder**\n- **Launch Date:** August 2025\n- **Concept:** Intelligent IDE with code understanding capabilities\n- **Key Features:**\n  - Multi-file editing\n  - Task delegation\n  - System architecture understanding\n  - Dependency relationship management\n  - Transparent collaboration\n- **Reception:** 588 upvotes (Featured)\n\nThe search didn't return a product specifically named \"full AI IDE,\" but these represent the major AI-focused IDE launches on Product Hunt in 2025. **Qoder** appears to have been the most popular among them with 588 upvotes.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
