        "content": "Web search results for query: \"new AI IDE launch February 2025 Windsurf Cursor alternative\"\n\nI'll perform a web search for information about a new AI IDE launched in February 2025 that's a Windsurf/Cursor alternative.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Zed编辑器更新：全新智能AI IDE - Cursor和Windsurf的替代品！完全免费！（开源）\",\"url\":\"https://post.m.smzdm.com/zz/p/a9k02noe/\"},{\"title\":\"cursor平替-windsurf无限续杯\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/lzy0214/article/details/154185157\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 评测：这款 人工智能 IDE 是你需要的颠覆性工具吗？\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7540645942061482018\"},{\"title\":\"Windsurf 下载和调试（超越cursor的免费的 AI IDE）\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/calvin189s/article/details/146425040\"},{\"title\":\"速递｜字节内部禁用第三方AI开发工具，自研AI IDE Trae将全面替代Cursor、Windsurf\",\"url\":\"https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20250529A02J9A00\"},{\"title\":\"AI IDE对比：Windsurf与Cursor的功能差异与实战体验\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/AzureMeadow65/article/details/154340203\"},{\"title\":\"Cursor不能用了？试试便宜量足的替代品 - Windsurf\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/heiyeshuwu/article/details/149491486\"},{\"title\":\"AI编程神器巅峰对决！Cursor、Windsurf、Trae谁将取代Copilot？实测结果颠覆认知！\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/qq_41687670/article/details/148747431\"}]\n\nBased on my search results, here's what I found about new AI IDEs launched as alternatives to Cursor and Windsurf:\n\n## Key Findings:\n\n### 1. **Zed Editor - Free Open-Source AI IDE**\n- A **Rust-based, open-source, free AI code editor** that now officially supports Windows\n- Positioned as a **free alternative** to both Cursor and Windsurf\n- Notable feature: **Privacy-focused design** where conversations don't get uploaded to the cloud\n- Source: Recent updates from November 2025\n\n### 2. **ByteDance's Trae**\n- **ByteDance internally developed an AI IDE called \"Trae\"**\n- The company is **banning third-party AI tools** (including Cursor and Windsurf) for employees\n- Trae is being promoted to replace these external AI coding tools internally\n- News reported in May 2025\n\n### 3. **Other AI IDE Alternatives Mentioned:**\n- **Bolt** - An AI programming assistant with context-aware code generation\n- **Augment Code** - Another competitor in the AI programming space\n- Chinese alternatives: 通义灵码 (Tongyi Lingma), Baidu Comate, JoyCoder, iFlyCode\n\n### Market Context:\nThe search results show that **Windsurf** (developed by Codeium) has emerged as a strong competitor to Cursor, with features like:\n- Multi-file context awareness\n- Agent system that autonomously breaks down complex tasks\n- GPT-5 support\n- Free tier availability\n\nHowever, the specific query about a \"new AI IDE launch in February 2025\" didn't return exact matches for that timeframe. The most relevant recent launches appear to be **Zed Editor** (with its AI features and Windows support) and **Trae** (ByteDance's internal tool).\n\nWould you like me to search for more specific information about any of these alternatives or explore a particular aspect of AI IDE launches in early 2025?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
